    <h3 class="right_title">
      <div class="position">当前位置：<a href="/" title="首页">首页</a> &gt; <a href="/list/?60_1.html">潍博之益</a>&gt; <a href="/list/?60_1.html">志愿者活动</a></div>
      <span>志愿者活动</span> </h3>
    <div class="clear"></div>
    <div class="active" id="shownews">
      <h1 class="title">潍博志愿者团队概述</h1>
      <div class="editor"><p><br/></p><p style="TEXT-INDENT: 24px"><span style="FONT-SIZE: 16px; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋; COLOR: rgb(0,0,0)"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋">潍坊市博物馆的志愿者工作始于</span>2008年</span><span style="FONT-SIZE: 16px; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋; COLOR: rgb(0,0,0)"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋">，近些年来</span></span><span style="FONT-SIZE: 16px; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋; COLOR: rgb(0,0,0)"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋">博物馆志愿</span></span><span style="FONT-SIZE: 16px; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋; COLOR: rgb(0,0,0)"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋">工作发展迅速，</span></span><span style="FONT-SIZE: 16px; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋; COLOR: rgb(0,0,0)"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋">由最初的几十人发展到</span>1</span><span style="FONT-SIZE: 16px; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋; COLOR: rgb(0,0,0)">8</span><span style="FONT-SIZE: 16px; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋; COLOR: rgb(0,0,0)">00余人，</span><span style="FONT-SIZE: 16px; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋; COLOR: rgb(0,0,0)"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋">包括</span></span><span style="FONT-SIZE: 16px; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋; COLOR: rgb(0,0,0)"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋">在校大学生、企事业单位干部职工、医生、教师、公安干警、退休老干部等社会各个层面</span></span><span style="FONT-SIZE: 16px; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋; COLOR: rgb(0,0,0)"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋">。这</span></span><span style="FONT-SIZE: 16px; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋; COLOR: rgb(0,0,0)"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋">支老、中、青志愿者队伍，年均服务</span></span><span style="FONT-SIZE: 16px; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋; COLOR: rgb(0,0,0)">5</span><span style="FONT-SIZE: 16px; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋; COLOR: rgb(0,0,0)">000余小时，讲解600余场次。先后开展的3·5雷锋日、风筝会、文博会、文展会、鲁台会、“5</span><span style="FONT-SIZE: 16px; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; COLOR: rgb(0,0,0)">•</span><span style="FONT-SIZE: 16px; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋; COLOR: rgb(0,0,0)">18”国际博物馆日、“文化遗产日”主题宣传活动</span><span style="FONT-SIZE: 16px; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋; COLOR: rgb(0,0,0)"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋">，</span></span><span style="FONT-SIZE: 16px; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋; COLOR: rgb(0,0,0)"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋">规范优质的服务得到了上级领导、广大市民的认可和赞扬。</span></span></p><p style="TEXT-INDENT: 36px"><span style="FONT-SIZE: 16px; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋; COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); LETTER-SPACING: 1px"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋">九年来</span></span><span style="FONT-SIZE: 16px; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋; COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); LETTER-SPACING: 1px"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋">先后有</span>50余名志愿者获得“潍坊市博物馆优秀志愿者”称号</span><span style="FONT-SIZE: 16px; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋; COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); LETTER-SPACING: 1px"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋">。</span></span><span style="FONT-SIZE: 16px; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋; COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); LETTER-SPACING: 1px"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋">志愿者</span></span><span style="FONT-SIZE: 16px; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋; COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); LETTER-SPACING: 1px"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋">周道瑜</span></span><span style="FONT-SIZE: 16px; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋; COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); LETTER-SPACING: 1px"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋">连续在博物馆志愿服务</span>5年获得“荣誉馆员”</span><span style="FONT-SIZE: 16px; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋; COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); LETTER-SPACING: 1px"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋">的荣誉</span></span><span style="FONT-SIZE: 16px; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋; COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); LETTER-SPACING: 1px"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋">，志愿者郝文芳在</span>“山东省第五届志愿讲解员大赛”中荣获二等奖，韩娜同志荣获得"2016山东省优秀志愿者先进个人"称号</span><span style="FONT-SIZE: 16px; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋; COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); LETTER-SPACING: 1px"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋">。并经潍坊市志愿者协会推荐加入第八届青年联合会委员。</span></span><span style="FONT-SIZE: 16px; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋; COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); LETTER-SPACING: 1px">2016年度志愿者团队中先后有</span><span style="FONT-SIZE: 16px; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋; COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); LETTER-SPACING: 1px"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋">刘晓丹、杨香玉等多</span></span><span style="FONT-SIZE: 16px; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋; COLOR: rgb(0,0,0)"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋">人</span></span><span style="FONT-SIZE: 16px; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋; COLOR: rgb(0,0,0)"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋">，</span></span><span style="FONT-SIZE: 16px; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋; COLOR: rgb(0,0,0)"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋">在</span></span><span style="FONT-SIZE: 16px; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋; COLOR: rgb(0,0,0)"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋">共青团市委在全市范围内开展的</span></span><span style="FONT-SIZE: 16px; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋; COLOR: rgb(0,0,0)"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋">学雷锋青年志愿服务活动中获得</span>“青年志愿服务之星”</span><span style="FONT-SIZE: 16px; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋; COLOR: rgb(0,0,0)"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋">的</span></span><span style="FONT-SIZE: 16px; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋; COLOR: rgb(0,0,0)"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋">称号</span></span><span style="FONT-SIZE: 16px; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋; COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); LETTER-SPACING: 1px"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋">。</span></span></p><p style="TEXT-INDENT: 32px"><span style="FONT-SIZE: 16px; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋; COLOR: rgb(0,0,0)"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋">我馆</span></span><span style="FONT-SIZE: 16px; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋; COLOR: rgb(0,0,0)"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋">志愿者工作的开展，进一步拉近了博物馆与公众的距离，而且让更多的人成为博物馆事业蓬勃发展的社会基础。</span></span></p><p style="TEXT-INDENT: 32px"><span style="FONT-SIZE: 16px; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋; COLOR: rgb(0,0,0)"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋">一</span></span><span style="FONT-SIZE: 16px; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋; COLOR: rgb(0,0,0)"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋">、博物馆志愿者的培训和管理</span></span></p><p style="TEXT-INDENT: 32px"><span style="FONT-SIZE: 16px; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋; COLOR: rgb(0,0,0)"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋">潍坊市博物馆对志愿者已建立了一套比较规范的培训体制。在师资上，除邀请了相关的专家学者之外，还特别注重本单位业务人员的培养锻炼，同时安排省、市讲解大赛中获奖的优秀讲解员进行示范讲解。主要培训内容包含专业知识学习</span></span><span style="FONT-SIZE: 16px; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋; COLOR: rgb(0,0,0)"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋">、</span></span><span style="FONT-SIZE: 16px; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋; COLOR: rgb(0,0,0)"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋">讲解技能培训</span></span><span style="FONT-SIZE: 16px; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋; COLOR: rgb(0,0,0)"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋">、</span></span><span style="FONT-SIZE: 16px; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋; COLOR: rgb(0,0,0)"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋">形体训练与礼仪知识的学习和培训</span></span><span style="FONT-SIZE: 16px; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋; COLOR: rgb(0,0,0)"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋">、</span></span><span style="FONT-SIZE: 16px; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋; COLOR: rgb(0,0,0)"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋">观摩点评、讲解实践与考核</span></span><span style="FONT-SIZE: 16px; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋; COLOR: rgb(0,0,0)"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋">等。</span></span></p><p><span style="FONT-SIZE: 16px; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋; COLOR: rgb(0,0,0)">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋">在</span></span><span style="FONT-SIZE: 16px; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋; COLOR: rgb(0,0,0)"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋">博物馆规范志愿者组织管理</span></span><span style="FONT-SIZE: 16px; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋; COLOR: rgb(0,0,0)"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋">方面，</span></span><span style="FONT-SIZE: 16px; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋; COLOR: rgb(0,0,0)"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋">制订《</span></span><span style="FONT-SIZE: 16px; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋; COLOR: rgb(0,0,0)"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋">潍博</span></span><span style="FONT-SIZE: 16px; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋; COLOR: rgb(0,0,0)"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋">志愿者章程》和《</span></span><span style="FONT-SIZE: 16px; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋; COLOR: rgb(0,0,0)"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋">潍博</span></span><span style="FONT-SIZE: 16px; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋; COLOR: rgb(0,0,0)"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋">志愿者手册》，建立志愿者服务登记制度。每年度进行优秀志愿者、明星志愿者和优秀志愿者团队的评比活动。在日常工作中</span>, 一方面为他们的学习和工作提供必要的条件，另一方面对他们严格要求、加强管理。从而使志愿者工作得以有效的运转，并持续不断地发展　</span></p><p style="TEXT-INDENT: 24px"><span style="FONT-SIZE: 16px; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋; COLOR: rgb(0,0,0)"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋">二</span></span><span style="FONT-SIZE: 16px; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋; COLOR: rgb(0,0,0)"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋">、潍坊市博物馆志愿者的主要工作内容</span></span></p><p style="TEXT-INDENT: 32px"><span style="FONT-SIZE: 16px; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋; COLOR: rgb(0,0,0)"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋">（一）义务讲解。义务讲解是志愿者最积极参与的一个重要方面。</span></span></p><p style="TEXT-INDENT: 24px"><span style="FONT-SIZE: 16px; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋; COLOR: rgb(0,0,0)"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋">（二）观众接待。志愿者的积极参与，为观众的参观提供更多的人文关怀，为弱势观众群体提供更贴心的人性化服务，从而更利于在博物馆营造一个整体和谐、温馨的参观环境。</span></span></p><p style="TEXT-INDENT: 24px"><span style="FONT-SIZE: 16px; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋; COLOR: rgb(0,0,0)"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋">（三）对外宣传。志愿者是博物馆联系社会最好的纽带和桥梁。组织志愿者走进社区，举行巡回展览、宣传活动和社会考察活动。他们的参与会把博物馆信息带到身边亲人、朋友及所在团体当中，无形中为博物馆赢得了口碑。博物馆志愿者也比一般社会公众更多更自觉地撰写新闻稿、感受性的文章，能广泛参与有关文化遗产、博物馆的节庆、展览等的专题宣传活动。</span></span></p><p style="TEXT-INDENT: 32px"><span style="FONT-SIZE: 16px; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋; COLOR: rgb(0,0,0)"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋">另外，博物馆</span></span><span style="FONT-SIZE: 16px; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋; COLOR: rgb(0,0,0)"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋">组织</span></span><span style="FONT-SIZE: 16px; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋; COLOR: rgb(0,0,0)"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋">志愿者也参与到在我馆</span></span><span style="FONT-SIZE: 16px; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋; COLOR: rgb(0,0,0)"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋">各类活动中来。如在</span></span><span style="FONT-SIZE: 16px; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋; COLOR: rgb(0,0,0)"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋">举办的大型展览中承担了在对外联络、组织观众、社会调查、活动策划、专题培训等工作。随着博物馆社会教育职能的不断拓展，志愿服务也更多参与到博物馆的各项工作中，例如图书资料的整理、翻译，归档等。</span></span></p><p style="TEXT-INDENT: 32px"><span style="FONT-SIZE: 16px; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋; COLOR: rgb(0,0,0)"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋">文化潍坊，魅力潍博</span></span><span style="FONT-SIZE: 16px; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋; COLOR: rgb(0,0,0)"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋">。</span></span><span style="FONT-SIZE: 16px; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋; COLOR: rgb(0,0,0)"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋">潍坊市博物馆志愿者组织将充分发挥博物馆自身专业特点和文化资源优势，打造文博志愿者团队品牌。</span></span><span style="FONT-SIZE: 16px; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋; COLOR: rgb(0,0,0)"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋">弘扬</span>“奉献、友爱、互助、进步”的志愿者精神，</span><span style="FONT-SIZE: 16px; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋; COLOR: rgb(0,0,0)"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋">为文明潍坊建设</span></span><span style="FONT-SIZE: 16px; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋; COLOR: rgb(0,0,0)"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋">体现新作为，做出新贡献。</span></span></p><p><span style="FONT-SIZE: 16px; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋">六一儿童节潍博志愿者团队举行</span>“牵手关爱-共享阳光”主题活动。</span><span style="FONT-SIZE: 16px; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋">志愿者邀请了我市特殊家庭、留守儿童</span>20余人来馆参观志愿讲解。</span></p><p><span style="FONT-SIZE: 16px; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋"></span>&nbsp;</p><p style="TEXT-ALIGN: center"><span style="FONT-SIZE: 16px; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋"><img title="1.jpg" alt="1.jpg" src="/upload/image/20161230/14830566954795194.jpg"/></span></p><p><span style="FONT-SIZE: 16px; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋"></span>&nbsp;</p><p style="TEXT-ALIGN: center"><span style="FONT-SIZE: 16px; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋">2016中秋节博物馆举办了诗歌朗诵会活动，志愿者们正在布置会场</span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p style="TEXT-ALIGN: center"><img title="2.jpg" alt="2.jpg" src="/upload/image/20161230/14830567625650755.jpg"/></p><p style="TEXT-ALIGN: center"><img title="3.jpg" alt="3.jpg" src="/upload/image/20161230/14830568348995955.jpg"/></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><span style="FONT-SIZE: 16px; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋">2016年3月5日学雷锋纪念日，我馆志愿者团队与山东交通职业学院共青团委联合开展了学雷锋活动，60余在校大学生在校团委书记谭勇的带领下集体报名加入到潍博志愿者团队中来。</span></p><p><span style="FONT-SIZE: 16px; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋"></span>&nbsp;</p><p style="TEXT-ALIGN: center"><img title="4.jpg" alt="4.jpg" src="/upload/image/20161230/14830569028165388.jpg"/></p><p style="TEXT-ALIGN: center"><span style="FONT-SIZE: 16px; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋">2016年5月4日青年志愿者们在博物馆合影</span></p><p><span style="FONT-SIZE: 16px; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋"></span>&nbsp;</p><p style="TEXT-ALIGN: center"><span style="FONT-SIZE: 16px; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋"><img title="5.jpg" alt="5.jpg" src="/upload/image/20161230/14830569959907957.jpg"/></span></p><p style="TEXT-ALIGN: center"><span style="FONT-SIZE: 16px; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋">我馆于每年三月份集中开展</span></span><span style="FONT-SIZE: 16px; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋">优秀志愿者</span></span><span style="FONT-SIZE: 16px; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋">评选暨</span></span><span style="FONT-SIZE: 16px; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋">颁奖仪式</span></span></p><p style="TEXT-ALIGN: center"><img title="6.jpg" alt="6.jpg" src="/upload/image/20161230/14830570709836409.jpg"/></p><p style="TEXT-ALIGN: center"><span style="FONT-SIZE: 16px; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋">志愿者参加岗前培训</span></span></p><p style="TEXT-ALIGN: center"><span style="FONT-SIZE: 16px; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋"><img title="7.jpg" alt="7.jpg" src="/upload/image/20161230/14830571367529966.jpg"/></span></span></p><p><span style="FONT-SIZE: 16px; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋"></span></span>&nbsp;</p><p style="TEXT-ALIGN: center; TEXT-INDENT: 32px"><span style="FONT-SIZE: 16px; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋">2016年我馆志愿者</span><span style="FONT-SIZE: 16px; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋">李道光</span></span><span style="FONT-SIZE: 16px; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋">在</span></span><span style="FONT-SIZE: 16px; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋">博物馆中秋诗歌会为</span></span><span style="FONT-SIZE: 16px; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋">观众义务书写</span></span><span style="FONT-SIZE: 16px; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋">古典</span></span><span style="FONT-SIZE: 16px; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋">诗词</span></span></p><p style="TEXT-INDENT: 32px"><span style="FONT-SIZE: 16px; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋"></span></span>&nbsp;</p><p style="TEXT-ALIGN: center"><img title="8.jpg" alt="8.jpg" src="/upload/image/20161230/14830572242132520.jpg"/></p><p style="TEXT-ALIGN: center; TEXT-INDENT: 32px"><span style="FONT-SIZE: 16px; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋">2016年10月我馆志愿者在“全国首家博物馆孔子学堂挂牌仪式</span><span style="FONT-SIZE: 16px; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋">”</span><span style="FONT-SIZE: 16px; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋">中志愿服务，并集体留影</span></span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p style="TEXT-ALIGN: center"><img title="9.jpg" alt="9.jpg" src="/upload/image/20161230/14830573124214292.jpg"/></p><p style="TEXT-ALIGN: center"><span style="FONT-SIZE: 16px; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋">我馆对志愿者进行服务设施技能培训</span></span></p><p><span style="FONT-SIZE: 16px; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋"></span></span>&nbsp;</p><p style="TEXT-ALIGN: center"><img title="10.jpg" alt="10.jpg" src="/upload/image/20161230/14830573871877912.jpg"/></p><p style="TEXT-ALIGN: center"><span style="FONT-SIZE: 16px; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋">2016年初我馆我馆为志愿者设立了志愿者餐厅</span></p><p style="TEXT-ALIGN: center"><img title="11.jpg" alt="11.jpg" src="/upload/image/20161230/14830574539666807.jpg"/></p><p style="TEXT-ALIGN: center"><span style="FONT-SIZE: 16px; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋">2016年度志愿讲解员参加培训</span></p><p style="TEXT-ALIGN: center"><img title="12.jpg" alt="12.jpg" src="/upload/image/20161230/14830575288872633.jpg"/></p><p style="TEXT-ALIGN: center"><span style="FONT-SIZE: 16px; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋">志愿者们在中秋诗歌会的现场</span></span></p><p><span style="FONT-SIZE: 16px; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋"></span></span>&nbsp;</p><p style="TEXT-ALIGN: center"><img title="13.jpg" style="HEIGHT: 465px; WIDTH: 679px" alt="13.jpg" src="/upload/image/20161230/14830575807664274.jpg" width="814" height="602"/></p><p style="TEXT-ALIGN: center"><span style="FONT-SIZE: 16px; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋">志愿者们在国际志愿者的集体宣誓仪式</span></span></p><p><span style="FONT-SIZE: 16px; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋"><img title="14.jpg" alt="14.jpg" src="/upload/image/20161230/14830576502595594.jpg"/></span></span></p><p style="TEXT-ALIGN: center"><span style="FONT-SIZE: 16px; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋"></span></span>&nbsp;</p><p style="TEXT-ALIGN: center"><span style="FONT-SIZE: 16px; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋">大学生志愿者担任旗手</span></span></p><p><span style="FONT-SIZE: 16px; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋"></span></span>&nbsp;</p><p><img title="15.jpg" alt="15.jpg" src="/upload/image/20161230/14830577179541426.jpg"/></p><p style="TEXT-ALIGN: center"><span style="FONT-SIZE: 16px; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋">潍博志愿者集体诗朗诵</span>“志愿服务</span><span style="FONT-SIZE: 16px; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style="FONT-SIZE: 16px; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋">爱的奉献</span>”</span></p><p><span style="FONT-SIZE: 16px; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋"></span>&nbsp;</p><p style="TEXT-ALIGN: center"><img title="16.jpg" alt="16.jpg" src="/upload/image/20161230/14830577838933882.jpg"/></p><p style="TEXT-ALIGN: center"><span style="FONT-SIZE: 16px; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋">志愿者日活动结束后志愿者们整理物品</span></span></p><p><span style="FONT-SIZE: 16px; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋"></span></span>&nbsp;</p><p style="TEXT-ALIGN: center"><img title="17.jpg" alt="17.jpg" src="/upload/image/20161230/14830578605193311.jpg"/></p><p style="TEXT-ALIGN: center; TEXT-INDENT: 32px"><span style="FONT-SIZE: 16px; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋">志愿者们在节日期间编排的手语舞</span>“有你的地方就是天堂”</span></p><p style="TEXT-INDENT: 32px"><span style="FONT-SIZE: 16px; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋"></span>&nbsp;</p><p><img title="18.jpg" alt="18.jpg" src="/upload/image/20161230/14830579339673399.jpg"/></p><p style="TEXT-ALIGN: center"><span style="FONT-SIZE: 16px; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋"></span></span>&nbsp;</p><p style="TEXT-ALIGN: center"><span style="FONT-SIZE: 16px; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋">志愿者古筝演奏</span></span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><script src="/inc/AspCms_VisitsAdd.asp?id=494"></script></div>
      
